item.title: How do i change the home and how can i move shops?[delta]
item.dc:creator: @I_D_D_S_I I D D S I
item.description:
@I_D_D_S_I wrote:

  1. Go to player.java search for toX = 3086+misc.random(3); toY = 3499+misc.random(3);
    change the toX to the Xcoord of your new home
    change the toY to the Ycoord of your new home.

  2. Go to autospawn. search the coords of your shops. change it to the coords of your new place.
